Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:58.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是什么值钱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.09,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
